      "text": "Producer \u2192 Consumer Chain:\n\n\u2022 orchestrator \u2192 00-scope.md \u2192 audit-context-building \u2192 01-context.md\n\u2022 invariant-writer consumes context \u2192 02-invariants.md\n\u2022 N \u00d7 invariant-catcher shards + hunt cards \u2192 03-findings-shard-<id>.md \u2192 merged \u2192 03-findings-raw.md\n\u2022 missing-validation-reasoning \u2192 04-validation-findings.md\n\u2022 protocol-reasoning \u2192 04a-reasoning-findings.md\n\u2022 orchestrator triages \u2192 05-findings-triaged.md\n\u2022 poc-writing + issue-writer + sherlock/cantina \u2192 CONFIRMED-REPORT.md",
